vernac_cmds: Lemma distinct_cons : forall (A : Setoid) (n : Nat) (v : seq n A), distinct v -> forall a : A, (forall i : fin n, ~ a =' v i in _) -> distinct (a;; v).
intro; case i; clear i; intro i; case i; clear i.
intros hi j; case j; clear j; intro j; case j; clear j.
intros i hi j; case j; clear j; intro j; case j; clear j.
red in |- *; intro; red in H0.
Lemma Seqtl_preserves_distinct : forall (A : Setoid) (n : Nat) (v : seq n A), distinct v -> distinct (Seqtl v).
apply H0 with (Build_finiteT (lt_n_S (S n1) (pred (S n0)) l0)) (Build_finiteT (lt_n_S 0 (pred (S n0)) l)); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (Seqtl v (Build_finiteT l0)); auto with algebra.
intros n1 l x0; case x0.
apply H0 with (Build_finiteT (lt_n_S _ _ l0)) (Build_finiteT (lt_n_S _ _ l)); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (Seqtl v (Build_finiteT l0)); auto with algebra.
Lemma omit_preserves_distinct : forall (A : Setoid) (n : Nat) (v : seq (S n) A), distinct v -> forall i : fin (S n), distinct (omit v i).
apply distinct_comp with (Seqtl v); auto with algebra.
apply distinct_comp with (head v;; omit (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n _ _ l))); auto with algebra.
intros n2 p' q; clear q.
red in |- *; red in H0; intro.
apply H0 with (Build_finiteT (lt_O_Sn (S n0))) (Build_finiteT (lt_n_S _ _ in_range_prf)); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (head v); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (Seqtl v (Build_finiteT in_range_prf)); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with ((head v;; omit (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n1 (S n0) l))) (Build_finiteT p')); auto with algebra.
cut (~ omit (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n1 (S n0) l)) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n _ _ l1)) =' head v in _).
generalize (omit_removes (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n1 (S n0) l)) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n2 n0 l1))).
cut (Seqtl v (Build_finiteT in_range_prf) =' head v in _).
cut (~ Build_finiteT (lt_n_S index (S n0) in_range_prf) =' Build_finiteT (lt_O_Sn (S n0)) in fin _).
apply H0 with (Build_finiteT (lt_n_S index (S n0) in_range_prf)) (Build_finiteT (lt_O_Sn (S n0))); auto.
apply Trans with (omit (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n1 (S n0) l)) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n2 n0 l1))); auto with algebra.
cut (~ omit (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n1 (S n0) l)) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n _ _ l0)) =' omit (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n1 (S n0) l)) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n _ _ l1)) in _).
unfold not in |- *; auto with algebra.
change (~ Seqtl v i1 =' Seqtl v j0 in _) in |- *.
Lemma distinct_omit_removes_all : forall (A : Setoid) (n : Nat) (v : seq (S n) A), distinct v -> forall (i : fin (S n)) (j : fin n), ~ omit v i j =' v i in _.
cut (~ Seqtl v j =' v (Build_finiteT in_range_prf) in _).
cut (~ v (Build_finiteT (lt_n_S _ _ in_range_prf0)) =' v (Build_finiteT in_range_prf) in _).
cut (~ Build_finiteT (lt_n_S index (S n0) in_range_prf0) =' Build_finiteT in_range_prf in fin _).
cut (~ v (Build_finiteT (lt_n_S _ _ l)) =' v (Build_finiteT in_range_prf) in _).
unfold not in |- *; auto with algebra.
cut (~ Build_finiteT (lt_n_S x0 (S n0) l) =' Build_finiteT in_range_prf in fin _).
cut ((head v;; omit (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n _ _ in_range_prf))) j =' v (Build_finiteT in_range_prf) in _).
apply H0 with (Build_finiteT (lt_O_Sn (S n0))) (Build_finiteT in_range_prf); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with ((head v;; omit (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n1 (S n0) in_range_prf))) (Build_finiteT l)); auto with algebra.
cut (omit (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n1 (S n0) in_range_prf)) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n _ _ l)) =' v (Build_finiteT in_range_prf) in _).
cut (omit (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n1 (S n0) in_range_prf)) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n _ _ l)) =' Seqtl v (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n _ _ in_range_prf)) in _).
apply H with (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n1 (S n0) in_range_prf)) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n2 n0 l)); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (v (Build_finiteT in_range_prf)); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with ((head v;; omit (Seqtl v) (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n n1 (S n0) in_range_prf))) (Build_finiteT l)); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (omit v (Build_finiteT in_range_prf) j); auto with algebra.
Lemma Map_embed_preserves_distinct : forall (A : Setoid) (n : Nat) (B : part_set A) (v : seq n B), distinct v -> distinct (Map_embed v).
apply H with i j; auto with algebra.
Lemma Map_embed_reflects_distinct : forall (A : Setoid) (n : Nat) (B : part_set A) (v : seq n B), distinct (Map_embed v) -> distinct v.
apply H with i j; auto with algebra.
Lemma seq_set_seq_preserves_distinct : forall (A : Setoid) (n : Nat) (v : seq n A), distinct v -> distinct (seq_set_seq v).
red in H; (apply (H _ _ H0); auto with algebra).
Lemma seq_set_seq_respects_distinct : forall (A : Setoid) (n : Nat) (v : seq n A), distinct (seq_set_seq v) -> distinct v.
red in H; (apply (H _ _ H0); auto with algebra).
Lemma cast_seq_preserves_distinct : forall (A : Setoid) (n m : Nat) (v : seq n A) (H : n =' m in _), distinct v -> distinct (cast_seq v H).
red in |- *; intro; red in H0; (apply H0 with (cast_fin i (sym_eq H)) (cast_fin j (sym_eq H)); auto with algebra).
generalize H1; elim i; elim j.
Lemma cast_seq_respects_distinct : forall (A : Setoid) (n m : Nat) (v : seq n A) (H : n =' m in _), distinct (cast_seq v H) -> distinct v.
red in |- *; intro; red in H0.
apply H0 with (cast_fin i H) (cast_fin j H).
generalize H1; elim i; elim j.
apply Trans with (Ap i); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (Ap j); auto with algebra.
